{
  "stem": "22883.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because I had to find right persons, you know, and therefore, it was required that I have to meet her several times.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And doing this several times of meeting her, which the situation changed differently-- it would be different.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I got interested in her as a-- as a young girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I liked her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then later on, I offered to-- to stay with her and to go somewhere where we could have more chance to-- to survive together.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, first we thought that maybe will be a good idea to go to the Russian partisans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard that in east of Poland, there are groups of Russian partisans which are fighting Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were quite-- both of us, she and I was quite naive and misinformed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know how it looks like and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were-- well, we tried, and we-- we started to arrange somehow to get to that places, which means east of-- of the occupied Poland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Apparently, it was-- well, almost ended in disaster, but somehow we managed to come out of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And do you want to have this situation described in detail?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go ahead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So because-- I will call Lillian-- Lillian is my wife and is the-- the Jewish girl which I met in 1943.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In 1939, she went to the part of Poland which was occupied by Bolsheviks, by Russians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because her uncle, a famous Jewish actor, Abram Morefski, he was at that time in Grodno.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Grodno was taken by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, and it's 1939, there were-- the-- the mail was still going from both sides of-- of Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
